    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant equipped with VarioCam Plus, delivering 315 hp with a high-revving, linear torque curve. The G96 6-speed manual transaxle offers precise shift gates and short throws, ensuring an engaging connection to the rear-wheel-drive layout. Crucially, the IMS bearing and Rear Main Seal (RMS) have been proactively addressed, mitigating common failure points of this engine architecture. The chassis maintains its composure through MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry, while the four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers provide exceptional clamping force and heat dissipation. A mechanically robust example with a clean underside, this 911 is tuned for the enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and tactile feedback over cosmetic perfection.",
